  "text": "Once again this recursive definition allows to eventually compute X x for any x, if p a < p {x} crit . By a simple recursion one easily notices that the values X x all belong to {0, 1}. Remark 4.2 Since the values X x all belong to {0, 1}, the min operator coincides with the product, and also with the \"and\" operator, interpreting the gas occupation as Boolean variables. Bousquet-Mélou [CITATION_1] when she considers the case (p 1 , p 2 , p 2 , p 2 ) in the square lattice case works under an equivalent model even if she uses a different vocabulary (we refer to Section 5.3 for some hints). ",
